Stop
Linux: $ ./jboss-cli.sh --connect command=:shutdown
Windows: > jboss-cli.bat --connect command=:shutdown

Restart
Linux: $ ./jboss-cli.sh --connect command=:reload
Windows: > jboss-cli.bat --connect command=:reload
